snippet.title: Epic Party Quest Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Epic Party Quest will go live on steam 12.02.2024!

Wishlist the game now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2024810?utm_source=trailer2023

Epic Party Quest is a local multiplayer party game for up to 4 players! Use your mobile phones as controllers, choose from many fast-paced mini-games and get the highest score to win!
